Package: zerra-system-cleaner
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Pardus Developer <developer@pardus.org.tr>
Depends: python3, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, policykit-1
Description: Pardus System Cleaner
 A lightweight and safe system cleaning utility designed for Pardus Linux.
 .
 This tool helps users recover disk space by cleaning:
  * APT cache and package archives
  * Old system logs and journals
  * Application caches (browser, thumbnail, etc.)
 .
 It features a native GTK interface that integrates seamlessly with
 the Pardus desktop environment, offering both manual and automatic
 maintenance options.
